content: wtfsayo: Merged 13 PRs this week with significant contributions including a major feature to show agent actions and runtime logs in UI (#3908, +31k/-12.6k lines), socket.io implementation to replace WebSockets (#3946), and several critical fixes for the core system and GUI. Consistently active across 6 days with a strong focus on bug fixes (43% of work) and infrastructure improvements, demonstrating a productive week with over 37k lines added across 694 modified files.
